    "en": {
      "title": "429 tear gas fired during the protest near the Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, 429 tear gas bullets and tear gas bombs were stolen from the police by the people who behaved riotously during the recent protest near the Parliament entrance road (Polduwa roundabout).",
        "It is reported that 340 tear gas bullets and 89 tear gas bombs were stolen.",
        "The police found 50 tear gas shells hidden in a house. The police have started investigations to find the other tear gas bullets and tear gas bombs."
      ],
